{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/extras/addtowishlist_gif_1.gif?t=1731122999\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is it?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mad Chess is a game that maintains standard chess rules while adding 19 more unique factions to the game. Factions have the same pawns and king as classic chess, but the 4 other pieces, while having the same movement patterns, trade their reduced range for RPG abilities that break specific chess rules.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This makes Mad Chess easy to learn but hard to master. With 190 match-ups instead of 1, chess just got its biggest expansion pack in centuries. Madness? No. Mad Chess. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/extras/good_scroll_1.gif?t=1731122999\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Twenty Factions, including:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <u>Humans</u>: Use the classic chess army that you all know with long-ranged units.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <u>Mermaids</u>: Bring the ocean with you by covering the chessboard with water.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <u>Angels</u>: Wield the Divine Light which grants protection &amp; situational invincibility.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <u>Dragons</u>: Gain necrotic bonuses upon having your units captured.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <u>Vampires</u>: Consume your own troops to gain momentum &amp; disturb enemy units.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Fairies</u>: Protect your archers to capture enemies without moving from afar. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Adventure</u>: 70+ missions campaign to help Princess Madeline vanquish the Silver Demons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Versus</u>: Play local games against a decent AI opponent (up to 1300 ELO) or another player. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Multiplayer</u>: Play public or private games online against other players with custom rules. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Shop</u>: Earn gold by playing to unlock factions and boards. (<strong>no microtransactions</strong>)</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731122999","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/page.bg.jpg?t=1731122999","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731122999","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731122999","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2053720,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551190/extras/addtowishlist_gif_1.gif?t=1731122999\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is it?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mad Chess is a game that maintains standard chess rules while adding 19 more unique factions to the game. Factions have the same pawns and king as classic chess, but the 4 other pieces, while having the same movement patterns, trade their reduced range for RPG abilities that break specific chess rules.  </p><p 